Package: pulldb-client
Version: 1.0.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: PestRoutes Engineering <engineering@pestroutes.com>
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31), bash, adduser
Provides: pulldb-cli
Homepage: https://github.com/CharlesHandshy/pullDB
Description: pullDB client CLI with embedded Python 3.12
 The standalone client CLI for pullDB.
 Installs to /opt/pulldb.client with embedded Python 3.12 runtime.
 Works on Ubuntu 20.04+ without requiring system Python 3.12.
